						<p>South wall of the <hi rend="italic">mahāmaṇḍapa</hi> of the Rāmaliṅgēśvara temple.</p>						

						<p>This undated record may be assigned to the 8th century on the basis of palaeography.</p>						

						<p>It mentions Śrī Kōchikīmuṇya Vamtāra of Sēnapankōṭa and seems to record his digging of the site.</p>						

